      • newIdlingResourceWatcher

        public static CapuccinoResourceWatcher newIdlingResourceWatcher(java.lang.Object resource)
        Returns a new CapuccinoResourceWatcher, which will be associated internally with a name derived from . Internally, this uses either the canonical or simple name of the resource's class, but this may change. Will return either a OperatingCapuccinoResourceWatcher if we're testing, or a NoOpCapuccinoResourceWatcher if we're in production. See isTesting().
        Parameters:
        resource - The object for which this CapuccinoResourceWatcher will be a member.
        Returns:
        an CapuccinoResourceWatcher.
